{"tid":37033,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"多虧三星告發 日本三電池廠遭歐盟罰款1.66億歐元","createTime":"2016-12-13T05:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T11:13:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ceb68c2bda9f53c94cf6465c7a39e8f9927bfe","tid":37033,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/24120458/samsung-sdi-e1479960308670.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2F24120458%2Fsamsung-sdi-e1479960308670.jpg&h=bb185587&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歐盟監管機構 12 日認定三陽電機（Sanyo Electric）、Sony、Panasonic 違法聯合操縱電話與筆電用鋰電池價格，3 家日廠合計挨罰 1.66 億歐元（約 1.75 億美元）。<br />\n<br />\n調查報告指出，上述公司以及三星 SDI 於 2004-2007 年間私下串連調高售價，並互相交換情報，如供需預測等敏感資訊，導致歐洲消費者權益受損。<br />\n<br />\n據華爾街日報報導，受懲處最重的三陽遭罰 0.97 億歐元，Panasonic、Sony 則分別被判罰 0.39 與 0.3 億歐元。<br />\n<br />\n三星 SDI 因提前揭露聯合壟斷而免責，躲過 0.58 億歐元的罰金。這已不是三星第一次，2010 年台灣 4 家面板廠就因三星告密而遭歐盟裁罰共 4.3 億歐元。"},{"pid":"f037c69f6f066001c2d25ff5a7252231aa628b9a","tid":37033,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80b3ce139aeab1945ef797d957ae43e77db408a","tid":37033,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:58:34.000Z","msg":"仆街自己肥完仲做25仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7435b3f6d52812022fbb78f9880c7f9c0400218","tid":37033,"uid":1979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆街自己肥完仲做25仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為佢既電池冇人買先告人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391